      "content": "it's just so scary because the things \"i\" am posting are starting to say stuff that's making people hate me, like things i would never actually say. it feels like this thing is actively trying to destroy my life. do you think there's a way to prove it's an AI and not me, or is the digital version of me already too far gone?",
